      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CLASSIC LASS (2) has a terrific record this track and trip with two wins and two placings from four starts. Comes off a (23.22) win last time, scoring by 0.8 lengths in a Grade 5 over 400m at this track. Looks suited and should go close. CINDY'S SECRET (1) had the drop on the lead and went on to be beaten 9 lengths into third (19.04) at this track in a Grade 5 over 318m. Well-placed to take this out. SPRING FRED (3) was safely held last time out, finishing eighth at this track over 318m behind Armoured Glass (19.27) in a Grade 5. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Expected to give a good account. HOLLY'S FOLLY (4) among the chances again based on last run here.",
